ncy of heavily absorbed sources (with NH ~10E22 - 10E24 cm-2) in our\nsample in comparison with the models. We therefore conclude that the synthesis\nmodels require some revision in their specific parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2004 21:08:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
