 computational studies of the origins and\nmacroevolution of terrestrial life.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2004 16:54:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 5 Feb 2005 05:23:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
